  A-tai7 si7 chit8 e5 ho5-khi3 ai2-ai2 chin u7 ti3-sek kap keng-giam7 e5 ni5-hoe3 e5 lang5.Tu2 tui3 chiN2 lai7 chhiuN7-chui2 to3 ti7 khng3 tiam3 chiN2-noa5-piN e5 chui2-koan3.A-tai7 tu2 chhiuN7-oan5 liau2 chui2, Tai7-pi2-tai7 toa3 chui2-koan3 tui3 cho2-pian (to3-peng5) jip8-lai5. Tai7-pi2-tai7 khoaN3-kiN3 A-tai7 ti7 hia chiu7 tiu5-tu5 chit8-e7, chong2-si7 A-tai7 giah8 thau5 chit8 e7 khoaN3, chiu7 eng7 bi5-chhio3 hoan-geng5 i. 
  A-tai7: Chu2 chiok-hok li2. 
