  A-tai7:Chiah nih joah8 e5 si5-chun7, khah ho2 tiam3 chia chhiuN7 moa2 li2 e5 chui2-koan3, theng3-hau7 hong5-hun am3 khah liang5 e5 si5-chun7, chiah thang kiaN5 khah hng7 e5 lou7 khi3 hia chhiuN7. 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: Chit khoan2 e5 cho3-hoat, si7 chit toe7-hng e5 hong-siok8 mah? 
