  A- tai7: Hoan-geng5 lin2 lai5 Su7-ka khia7-khi2, chhiaN2 che7, siN-hun7 lang5! (In chiu7 saN-kap che7 ti7 cheN2-noa5-teng2). Goan2 Su7-ka lang5 tui3 Sa-ma2-li7-a tong5-chok8, kau3-taN long2 si7 iu2-sian7--e5, (iu-siong e5 chhio3) tong-jian5 Iu5-thai3 lang5 long2 siam2-pi7 goan2, chi3-chio2 iah8 m7 hou7 goan2 e5 khi3-sek jia-kham3 ti7 in ka2-chong keng3-khian5 e5 keng-thau5-teng2. 
