  A-tai7: Ka7 goa2 kong2 ti7 Ka-li7-li7 e5 chong7-hong2, in-ui7 goa2 chin ku2 m7-bat kap tui3 hia lai5 e5 lang5 tam5-lun7 chiah e5 oe7. 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: Hian7-chai7 sou2 u7 e5 hiong-bin5 tou ui7-tioh8 chit8 ui7 ka-ki7 toan3-gian5 I si7 Bi2-sai3-a e5 bak8-chhiuN7 teh toa7 heng-hun3 lioh! 
  A-tai7: Sou2 eng3-un2 e5 kiam2 m7-si7 I mah? 
