  A-tai7: Si7, ti7 Ki-li2-sim soaN; thiaN-kiN3 kong2 hia boe7 thang chhin-chhiuN7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 e5 tong5-hong5, chong2-si7 hia goan2 e5 chou2 Nga2-kok bat ti7 hia keng3-pai3, ia7 li7 goa2 e5 chou2 Nga2-kok sou2 kut8 e5 chui2-chiN2 bo5 hng7. Tng Bi2-sai3-a kang3-lim5 e5 si5-chun7, I iah8 koh lim5-kau3 chit8 e5 sou2-chai7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chiuN7 Ia5-lou7-sat-leng2 chit8-poaN-iuN7. 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: Goa2 iah8 an2-ni siuN7, goa2 ke-lai7 e5 kiaN2-ji5 thang kau3 hia hak8-sip8 mah? 
