  Ko-biat8: Ouh! A-tai7, thiaN ou3! Che chiaN3 si7 toa7 su7-kiaN7, tu2-chiah goa2 kiaN5 ke-lou7 e5 si5-chun7, goa2 chhin-bak8 khoaN3-kiN3 Tai7-li7-liap8; goa2 sim-lai7 ki5-koai3, i cha7-jit8 chiah tu2-tioh8 piN phah, iau2 u7 chit khoan2 e5 taN2-liong7 thang koh lai5 chia. Chong2-si7 m7-si7 ah! I chit8 e7 khoaN3-tioh8 goa2, chiu7 lip8-khek oat8 ke3 ke-lou7 kau3 phian-piN-lou7 khi3. Goa2 siuN7, i phah-sng3 m7-kaN2 koh-chai3 kun7-oa2 lan2, chong2-si7 i kau3 an-un2 e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7 hoe5-thau5, chhui3 chhut ok-gian5, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 tim3 chioh8-thau5 chit8-iuN7. 
  A-tai7: Goa2 siuN7, lan2 m7 chun2 i lai5 chia chhiuN7 chui2 si7 thai3 bo5 jin5-cheng5 e5 cho3 hoat; chiah-nih joah8 e5 thiN-khi3 khi3 Nga2-kok e5 chiN2 si7 siong-tong e5 hng7 lou7, lian5 lan2 ka-ki7 ia7 boe7-oe7 chhi3 siuN7 kiaN5 chiah hng7 lou7 neh. 
  Ko-biat8: Goa2 m7-ku2 chin ai3 hou7 chit khoan2 phaiN2 hu7-jin5-lang5, chai7-lai5 bo5 u7 chit8 e5 chhin-chhiuN7 i, sou2-i2 hou7 i khi3 kiaN5 hng7 lou7, lan2 m7-bian2 khi3 koan2 i, kiam2-chhai2 Siong7-te3 oe7 phah-si2 i, hou7 lan2 thang kap chit ho7 chhiong-ki thoat-li7 koan-he7 lah. 
  A-tai7: Ai-ioh! Ko-biat8! M7-thang kong2 phaiN2 oe7, i ma7 li2 e5 si5-chun7 li2 chaiN2-iuN7? 
  Ko-biat8: (Tek-i3 e5 chhio3) Ouh, goa2 choe3 pi2 ma7 koh-khah li7-hai7 e5 su7: goa2 hiong3 i tim3 chioh8-thau5, jian5-au7 bu2-jiok8 i. 
  A-tai7: Li2 kiu3-keng3 si7 chit8 e5 thih-sim, chioh8-tng5, khok-heng5 e5 lang5. Ko-biat8! Lai5 ou3, lai5 kap chit ui7 poaN lai5 chia kap lan2 cho3 chhu3-piN saN-kap khia7 e5 siN-hun7-lang5 kiN3 bin7 chit8-e7 (Tai7-pi2-tai7 i2-keng chhiuN7 oan5 liau2 chui2, cheng7-cheng7 thiaN in e5 tam5-oe7). 
  Ko-biat8: Goan7 Chu2 chiok-hok li2, siN-hun7-lang5! 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: Goan7 Chu2 chiok-hok li2, hit ui7......li2 tu2-chiah the5-khi2 e5 hit ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5......chia u7 chin-choe7 chhin-chhiuN7 i e5 mah? 
  Ko-biat8: Bo5, bo5, chi2-u7 chit8 e5, chiu7-si7 i, put-ko3 goan2 koh bo5 ku2 oe7 chiong i koaN2 chau2, m7-chun2 i kun7 che chiN2, che chi2 si7 chhou-pou7 e5 choe3-hoat. 
  A-tai7: Tai7-pi2-tai7, goa2 sim-lai7 it-tit8 siuN7 hit ui7 jia2-khi2 su7-kiaN7 e5......li2 siuN7 I oe7 kiaN5-koe3 che tiau5 lou7 lai5 mah? 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: Goa2 khak-sin3 I it-teng7 boe7 oe7 lai5, chhi3-siuN7 I si7 lu5-thai3 lang5, chiah e5 hak8-su7 iu7 chiam7-chiam7 chin teh siu7-khi3 I lai5, kiam2-chhai2 hian7-chai7 I i2-keng bo5 ti7 se3-kan lah. 
  A-tai7: Sian-ti sou2 ki3-chai3 e5 si5-hau7 kun7 lah (i chu3-sin5 khoaN3 hng7 e5 sou2-chai7 ka-ki7 kong2), siat-su2 lan2 bo5 kiN3 I chiu7 u7 chai-e7 lah. 
  Ko-biat8: (Heng-hun3 tioh8) KhoaN3! KhoaN3 i lai5 lah. Tai7-li7-liap8 lai5 lah, i eng7 chau2--e5 lai5. Oh! Ho2 toa7 taN2, keng3 kaN2 tui3 chit tiau5 lou7 lai5! Lan2 ka7 koaN2 i chau2. Tai7-pi2-tai7, li2 kap A-tai7, goa2, saN-kap lai5 ti2-khong3 i. 
  (Tai7-li7-liap8 chau2 chiuN7 tai5, heng-hun3 tioh8, u7 si5 gim7 kun5-thau5-bu2, khui tioh8 chhiu2). 
