  Ko-biat8: Goa2 kong2, khi3, khi3! Li2 lian5 chui2-koan3 to bo5 toa3 leh, koh khah bo5 li2-iu5 tiam3 chia sun5-lai5 sun5-khi3, khi3, khi3! 
