  Tai7-li7-liap8: (Seng5-khun2 teh khoaN3 i). Li2 bo5 siuN7 ai3 chai-iaN2; in-ui7 li2 e5 sim phaiN2, li2 tui3 goa2 toa7 chan5-jim2 lah; na7 si7 kui2-tiam2-cheng cheng5 goa2 oe7 thai5-si2 li2. TaN hian7-chai7......ui7 sim2-mih8 nih? Ko-biat8! Goa2 hoan2-tng2 thiaN3 li2. 
