  Tai7-li7-liap8: Lai5! Lai5! Lai5 khoaN3 Bi2-sai3-a lah. (I khan Ko-biat8 e5 chhiu2, chit pai2 bo5 haiN3 chau2). 
  Ko-biat8: Goa2 beng5-pek8 I si7 Bi2-sai3-a. I ki3-jian5 oe7-thang ka7 li2 sia3-bian2; goa2 che bat tui3 li2 thai3 chan5-jim2 e5 lang5, un2-tang3 I ia7 beh sia3-bian2 goa2 lah! Tai7-li7-liap8! 
  A-tai7: (A-tai7 khoaN3 in li7-khui, Tai7-li7-liap8 khan iau2 teh chhng3-chhng3 hau2 e5 Ko-biat8). 
  A-tai7: (Oat8-thau5 khoaN3 Tai7-pi2-tai7 kong2). Kho2-leng5 i chiu7-si7 tu2-chiah sou2 the5-khi2 e5 hit ui7 Bi2-sai3-a oh! 
  Tai7-pi2-tai7: (Bo5 khak-sit8 e5 khoan2-sit), chong2-si7 goa2 ...... goa2 m7 chai-iaN2, kiam2-chhai2 si7! Goa2 na2 chun2 iau2 ki3-tit; i u7 i-ho2 phoa3-piN7 lang5, hou7 pai2-kha e5 oe7 kiaN5 lou7, chheN-me5 e5 oe7 khoaN3-kiN3, chhau3-hiN7 e5 oe7 thiaN-kiN3, si2-lang5 oe7 koh-oah8; lan2 lai5-khi3, lai5-khi3 khoaN3 ah! 
  A-tai7: Ho2! Lan2 lai5 khi3, lan2 thang chit8 lou7 thoan5-po3 che ho2 siau-sit hou7 lang5 chai-iaN2. 
